Interface GraphWalker.NextNodeSelector<NodeNameType>

  • Type Parameters:
    NodeNameType - The datatype for the graph's node's names
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphWalker.RandomWalker
    Enclosing class:
    GraphWalker<NodeNameType>

    public static interface GraphWalker.NextNodeSelector<NodeNameType>
    This interface defines the method needed by the GraphWalker class to implement all features of graph walking _except_ the algorithm used to select the next node to visit
